## EXAMPLE OF GOOD VS BAD

**BAD:**
- Title: `Cat Eye Nails: Every Style, Color & Design Worth Trying in 2026` (65 chars, used for 8 different pages)
- Description: `Cat eye nails in 2026 are sharper and more wearable than ever. Here is every style worth knowing.` (97 chars but generic, no trigger, restates title)

**GOOD:**
- Title: `Galaxy Cat Eye Nails: The Multi-Chrome Effect That Shifts in Light` (66 chars — trim to: `Galaxy Cat Eye Nails: Multi-Chrome That Shifts in Every Light` = 61 chars)
- Description: `Most cat eye nails look flat indoors. Galaxy cat eye shifts color in every light — here's how to find your version.` (116 chars, names the problem, promises resolution)

